  "texts": [
    "Conversely, systolic array cores are utilized for dynamic computation in MHA, non-linear operations such as softmax and layer normalization, and LoRA computation if considering the fine-tuning phase.",
    "MMsystolic = 𝑂(𝑑 𝑚𝑜𝑑𝑒𝑙.",
    "𝑛 2) + 2𝑘 × 𝑂(𝑑 𝑚𝑜𝑑𝑒𝑙.",
    "𝑟. 𝑛) + +3 × 𝑂(𝑑 𝑚𝑜𝑑𝑒𝑙.",
    "𝑛)The MMsystolic includes the operations MHA-2, LoRA, and nonlinear computations MHA-3, L1, and L2."
  ]
